@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eedvtx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.85 * v2 + 0.88)) / v1)
    v2 = (wp.sin(v2) / 0.09)
    v2 = (wp.abs(0.68) / v1)
    v0 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.71 / v2 + 0.26)) - v0)
    data[tid] = v0
